Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:06.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:17.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:26.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:30.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:35.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:41.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:48.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:53.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:55.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:01:03.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.43,0:01:12.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:16.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:21.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:28.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:34.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:39.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:41.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:45.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:49.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:52.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:54.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:55.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:57.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:59.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:01.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:05.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:08.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:14.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:19.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:25.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:32.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we take down Moria?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Not Out of Danger Yet!\NOrders to Annihilate the Straw Hat Crew!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their bodies are vanishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Didn't we win?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang it! Were we too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're vanishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:05:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we won, darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:11.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Pirate Ship on the Grand Line"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:13.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:16.19,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come to the deck, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit being stupid and hit the hay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The morning light will fry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been two years since Moria\Nstole our shadows. We'll never...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Captain, please take a look at my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have... a shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet your shadow has also returned, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-O-Our...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our shadows are back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's everyone, Captain!\NAll of our shadows have come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:06:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, do you think someone defeated Moria?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so powerful that he went up\Nagainst Kaido of the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could possibly take out Moria?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:20.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Somewhere in the West Blue\Non the Grand Line"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's back! I have a shadow again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many years has it been\Nsince I've seen the light of day?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our zombies in Thriller Bark\Nfinally kicked the bucket!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're free from Moria's curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can watch the sunrise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! I have a shadow! It's following me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a reflection!\NI can see myself in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What was all that\Ncommotion about, Margarita?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My shadow! My shadow has come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Your shadow has returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As in the shadow that was stolen\Nby pirates ten years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so surprised that I accidentally\Ndropped your prized dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true I had hard feelings\Ntowards plates, but I've reformed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am really sorry. I will leave\Nthe manor immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about those plates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, this calls for a celebration!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is truly wonderful, Margarita.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it great, Margarita?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very much alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a second, I thought I\Nwas about to go to Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good to me! If we can go together,\NI'd love to go to Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't funny, you jerks!\NWe seriously thought you were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You nearly vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness! That was bad for my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:09:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, not that I have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the morning sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid of the sunrise anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can kiss goodbye to life in the dark forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray! Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like all of them are okay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We nearly ceased to exist\Nwhen the morning light hit us,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but our bodies were fully restored when
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nour shadows returned just in the nick of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably along the same lines of\Nhow Moria could alter a body's shape
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by manipulating its shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I make his shadow round...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Oars will turn into a ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oars Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I know is that our bodies\Nand shadows have to match.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax! This is the only time we're ever gonna have the fun
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of losing our shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm just glad we didn't lose anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of a sudden, I feel totally wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There any cola around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the strange creatures and phenomena\Nwe've seen since coming ashore
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were nothing more than\Na ruse put on by Moria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that he has been defeated,\Nthere is nothing left on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like waking from a nightmare in\Nthe morning, everything has vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, this was one nasty haunted mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey! Wake up, Absalom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Absalom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off! I'm not going to marry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has already lost her shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hogback?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the record, what happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what happened to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd wager someone defeated you. Pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly,\NI have bad news about Moria-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat defeated Moria-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Not so loud! Lower the volume!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so riled up, Hogback?\NYou should be called Rileback.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thriller Bark is of no use to me now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't plan on spending\Nthe rest of my days as a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Luffy shrink back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me that after he uses the Giant Gear,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his body shrinks for however\Nlong he used that gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think Luffy's new fighting\Nstyle is too hard on his body?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the enemies waiting ahead of us\Nonly continue to get stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's gonna keep pushing himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to pull our own weight better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them still has its shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm a severely injured old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's confusing! Just pass\Nyourself off as a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the old man\Nwe met at the graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it! I never dreamed I would
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:13:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,see the day I could walk under the sun again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! How can I ever repay you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Grandpa Spoil!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honorary President of the Victim Association!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, guys! So you pulled through?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Come to think of it,\Nwe still haven't thanked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're grateful from the bottom of our hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for all the trouble we've caused you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we saw all the mayhem you caused,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we figured if you couldn't do it, no one could!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one in Thriller Bark's Victim Association...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will ever forget the debt we owe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is anything you'd like,\Nplease say the word!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't much,\Nbut we have some food reserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better yet, you're welcome to marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We'll pass!\N--Five men turned her down all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been rejected 4,449 times!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't need to thank us...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what Luffy said, Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm especially interested in you!\N--We simply fought to suit our own needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Will you marry me?\N--We just saved you while we were at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say that?!\NThey actually want to thank us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You should listen to her, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us do something for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't care if you\Nsaved us on the side or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're grateful that you defeated Moria.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Why don't you swipe\Nall of Moria's treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll load it onto your ship for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's already on...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! I forgot about something important!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had totally forgotten about him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds as though my fears were justified.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it would seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:16:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, remain calm and hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During our fight with Moria...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I forgot to mention this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is one more member on this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of the Seven Warlords!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Warlord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are two of the Seven Warlords\Ndoing on the same island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have finally found a\Nreplacement for Crocodile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would look bad if another one of the\NSeven Warlords needed to be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he still breathing, even if barely?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he is still alive, I would\Nlike to wait for his recovery
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and let him retain his position as one\Nof the Seven Warlords for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can take further measures later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we lose one Warlord after the next,\Nthe title will cease to demand respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This information must not get out to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, those pirates\Ncause nothing but trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I recognize him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nearly as large as Moria,\Nthat pirate was called the "Tyrant."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Bartholomew Kuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.83,0:17:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Tyrant Kuma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the pirate whose\Ncruelty knows no bounds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand what I'm saying, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not leave witnesses to testify\Nthat Straw Hat defeated Moria.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The World Government is\Nassigning you a special mission:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annihilate everyone on the island,\Nincluding the Straw Hat Crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He just said "annihilate."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, wait! Is he gonna annihilate...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...all of us?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just got free from Moria's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:19:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! We can't fight two Warlords in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took all we had just to defeat Moria.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, get back! I'll take him on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful! He uses some sort of power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw someone vanish when\Nhe touched her with his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Negative Ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Special Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The people he touches vanish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:20:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he can also warp.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the Cat Burglar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're part of the Straw Hat Crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that Monkey D. Luffy\Nhas an older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives?! He got up there\Nin the blink of an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a freak on our hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His hands... are dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When'd he get down here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'd definitely call that warping.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! We were finally set free!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way I'm gonna die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I'll never let someone stand\Nbetween us and our voyage ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you heard them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:22:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, men! You don't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.81,0:22:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He pierced through the whole group\Nwithout even touching all of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate Hunter Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.97,0:23:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will start with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is with the padding\Non the palms of his hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It repels all of my attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is my ability. Your time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.75,0:23:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"When it rains, it pours."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.43,0:23:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.15,0:23:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die, then that shows the limit of my ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.77,0:23:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It Repels Everything!\NKuma's Paw-Paw Power!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.15,0:23:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
